text: Patrycja Królikowska (born 15 May 1992) is a Polish handball player for Vistal Gdynia and the Polish national team.EHF profile She participated at the 2016 European Women's Handball Championship.2016 European Championship roster ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female handball players Category:Sportspeople from Łódź
